OMP's amazing attribute with respect to\ndynamic range.\n  Detailed comparisons with existing algorithms such as Spectral Iterative Hard\nThresholding (SIHT) and the frame-adapted BP are given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 25 Jun 2011 22:53:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-28"}
