on of stability\nof the symmetric solitons appears with the increase of the overlap degree. In\nthe case of a moderately strong overlap, another SSB effect is found, in the\nform of a pair of symmetry-breaking and restoring bifurcations which link\nfamilies of the symmetric and asymmetric solitons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Jun 2011 11:15:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
